        <title>Data Visualization Dashboard</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/projects/data-viz-dashboard/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/projects/data-viz-dashboard/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="http://localhost:1313/dashboard-cover.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Data Visualization Dashboard" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;project-description&#34;&gt;Project Description
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;An interactive web-based dashboard that helps users analyze and visualize complex datasets with ease. Built with modern web technologies for optimal performance and user experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;tech-stack&#34;&gt;Tech Stack
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Frontend&lt;/strong&gt;: React, TypeScript, D3.js&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Backend&lt;/strong&gt;: Node.js, Express&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Database&lt;/strong&gt;: PostgreSQL, Redis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deployment&lt;/strong&gt;: Docker, AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;features&#34;&gt;Features
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;real-time-data-processing&#34;&gt;Real-time Data Processing
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Process and visualize streaming data in real-time with WebSocket connections.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;interactive-charts&#34;&gt;Interactive Charts
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Line charts with zoom and pan&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Heatmaps with custom color schemes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3D surface plots&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network graphs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;export-options&#34;&gt;Export Options
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PDF reports&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CSV data export&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;PNG/SVG chart export&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shareable links&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;screenshots&#34;&gt;Screenshots
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gallery&#34;&gt;
    
![Dashboard Overview](overview.png)
*Main dashboard view with multiple widgets*

![Analytics](analytics.png)
*Detailed analytics panel*


&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;code-example&#34;&gt;Code Example
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Here&amp;rsquo;s a snippet of the custom D3 chart component:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;
&lt;table class=&#34;lntable&#34;&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&#34;lntd&#34;&gt;
&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 1
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 2
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;lnt&#34;&gt; 3
